OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPolice in England and Wales
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto get anti-racism training
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Police officers in England and Wales   
OL,6, will be given mandatory anti-racism    
OL,7, training under a new plan to tackle    
OL,8, racism, discrimination and bias.       
OL,10,FThe National Police Chiefs Council     
OL,11,F(NPCC) wants to recruit more black     
OL,12,Fofficers and staff, and improve black  
OL,13,Fpeople's confidence in the police.     
OL,15,FConfidence levels are about 64% among  
OL,16,Fblack communities, compared with an    
OL,17,Faverage of 74%.                        
OL,19,FThe NPCC says its Race Action Plan is  
OL,20,Fnot about "being woke".                
